### ============================================================
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### capture tokens
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}
@refreshToken = {{login.response.body.data.refreshToken}}
### ============================================================
### US-PROFILE-01 — View own profile
### Requires a valid accessToken (run auth.http → login first, or set it
### manually in the environment via REST Client's "Set Environment Variable").
### ============================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### ============================================================
### US-PROFILE-01 — Update own profile (landlord: fullName / phone)
### ============================================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "{{fullName}} Updated",
  "phone": "0901234567"
}

###

### Update with no body / invalid (expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "Tenant"
}

###

### Unauthenticated request (expect 401 UNAUTHENTICATED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile

###
